translatedContent: # Minecraft 服务器网页管理面板

originContent: A **lightweight** Minecraft server web management panel with modern UI and comprehensive server management features.
translatedContent: 一款 **轻量级** 的 Minecraft 服务器网页管理面板，拥有现代化的用户界面和全面的服务器管理功能。

originContent: - **Server Download** Support for downloading specific server versions directly from the management page
translatedContent: - **服务器下载** 支持在管理页面直接下载指定版本的服务器

originContent: - **Server Version Switching** Support for one-click server version switching
translatedContent: - **服务器版本切换** 支持一键切换服务器版本
- **一键启动/停止/重启** Minecraft 基岩版服务器

originContent: - **Real-time Status Monitoring** Display server running status
translatedContent: - **实时状态监控** 显示服务器运行状态
- 游戏模式（生存/创造/冒险）
- 难度设置（和平/简单/普通/困难）

originContent: - **Server Configuration File Management** Automatically maintains `server.properties` file
translatedContent: - **服务器配置文件管理** 自动维护 `server.properties` 文件

originContent: - **Add/Remove Players** Manage the list of players allowed to join the server
translatedContent: - **添加/移除玩家** 管理允许加入服务器的玩家列表
- **白名单文件管理** 自动维护 `allowlist.json` 文件

originContent: - **Player Permission Settings** Assign permission levels to specific players
translatedContent: - **玩家权限设置** 为特定玩家分配权限等级
- **权限文件管理** 自动维护 `permissions.json` 文件

originContent: - **World File Upload** Support for `.zip` and `.mcworld` formats with automatic extraction
translatedContent: - **世界文件上传** 支持 `.zip` 和 `.mcworld` 格式并自动解压

originContent: - **World Switching** One-click activation of different worlds
translatedContent: - **世界切换** 一键激活不同世界

originContent: - **World Deletion** Safe deletion of unwanted world files
translatedContent: - **世界删除** 安全删除不需要的世界文件

originContent: - **Current World Identification** Clear display of the currently active world
translatedContent: - **当前世界识别** 清晰显示当前激活的世界

originContent: - **Resource File Upload** Support for `.zip` and `.mcpack` formats
translatedContent: - **资源文件上传** 支持 `.zip` 和 `.mcpack` 格式

originContent: - **Resource Activation** One-click activation of different resource packs
translatedContent: - **资源激活** 一键激活不同资源包

originContent: - **Resource Deletion** Safe deletion of unwanted resource packs
translatedContent: - **资源删除** 安全删除不需要的资源包

originContent: - **Real-time Log Viewing** Monitor Minecraft server logs in real-time through the web interface
translatedContent: - **实时日志查看** 通过网页界面实时监控 Minecraft 服务器日志

originContent: - **Auto-scroll** Option to automatically scroll to the latest log entries
translatedContent: - **自动滚动** 可选自动滚动至最新日志条目

originContent: - **Direct Command Input** Execute Minecraft server commands directly from the web interface
translatedContent: - **直接命令输入** 通过网页界面直接执行 Minecraft 服务器命令

originContent: - **Command History** View and reuse previously executed commands
translatedContent: - **命令历史** 查看并重用之前执行的命令

originContent: - **Quick Commands** Access frequently used commands through categorized quick access buttons
translatedContent: - **快速命令** 通过分类快速访问按钮访问常用命令

originContent: - **Login System** Secure access to the management panel with password authentication
translatedContent: - **登录系统** 通过密码认证安全访问管理面板

originContent: - **Session Management** Automatic session handling with secure token-based authentication
translatedContent: - **会话管理** 自动会话处理，基于安全令牌认证

originContent: - **Access Control** Protect server management functions from unauthorized access
translatedContent: - **访问控制** 保护服务器管理功能免受未授权访问
- **操作系统**：Windows 10 及以上或 Ubuntu 18.04 及以上（Linux）
- **网络**：开放端口 8080（管理面板）和 19132（Minecraft 服务器）

originContent: - Download the appropriate version for your operating system from the [Releases](https://github.com/ckfanzhe/bedrock-easy-server/releases) page
translatedContent: - 从[版本](https://github.com/ckfanzhe/bedrock-easy-server/releases)页面下载适合您操作系统的版本

translatedContent: - 服务器数据将保存在 `./data` 目录中

translatedContent: - 构建 Vue.js 前端（`npm run build`）

originContent: - Copy built assets to the embed directory
translatedContent: - 将构建好的资源复制到嵌入目录

originContent: - Compile Go binaries for all platforms with embedded frontend
translatedContent: - 编译包含嵌入前端的所有平台的 Go 二进制文件

originContent: **Note**: The build process now includes frontend compilation using webpack, which bundles all Vue.js components, styles, and assets into optimized files that are then embedded into the Go binary for single-file deployment.
translatedContent: **注意**：构建过程现在包括使用 webpack 进行前端编译，将所有 Vue.js 组件、样式和资源打包成优化后的文件，然后嵌入到 Go 二进制文件中，实现单文件部署。
